\n至於其他輪商安排，法興證券。。。。。。。。。"},{"pid":"8a0cac1ff2cd77b65d06c4b37dd815007cb001ad","tid":2362379,"uid":271130,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-11T11:47:32.000Z","msg":"供成點算<br />\n<br />\n仲點搵食<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a08f34f373db89da608a36a2bf8e1cdc40b51f5d","tid":2362379,"uid":96548,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-11T11:50:18.000Z","msg":"供成又贏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d3cd6523a1d0fef5e4fb54796aa5c8b76c6e6486","tid":2362379,"uid":51701,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"8a0cac1ff2cd77b65d06c4b37dd815007cb001ad","tid":2362379,"uid":271130,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-11T11:47:32.000Z","msg":"供成點算<br />\n<br />\n仲點搵食<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-11T11:52:13.000Z","msg":"50 年後笑到最後"}]}